      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COPYCAT (9) is a former NSW galloper heading to the NT poised to win after two runs back, the latest placing at Gosford. Best figures more than measure up and expected to run well first try on the dirt. OCEAN'S JEN (7) was a big winner two back then safely held in tougher grade last time. Back a notch and gets a chance to atone. IF I WAS YOU (2) resumes from a spell of nine weeks and is having his first outing under new trainer Chloe Baxter. Former Victorian who can measure up at the first run for a new barn. DYNAMIC THEORY (1) has been in good form, scoring three back at this track then placing twice in a row, most recently when second over 1200m at this track. Drawn for a soft run and can continue the good form.",
